uenced by her spirituality, and his teachings are often considered a continuation of her "Little Way." *[[Jean Vanier]] – founder of l'Arche *[[Alphonsa]] – First Indian Saint<ref>http://www.syromalabarchurch.in/saints.php?saintname=saintalphonsa&page=message.</ref> *[[Anna Schaffer]] – German Saint *[[Jack Kerouac]], American author <ref>[https://www.nytimes.com/books/first/m/miles-kerouac.html. Miles, Barry. "Jack Kerouac King of the Beats", ''The New York Times - Books'', 1999]</ref>
